              "path": ["api", "v1", "product-media", "65abc123def456789012347"]
            },
            "description": "Delete a media (soft delete + file removal)\n\n**Auth**: Requires Admin token\n**Note**: File is deleted from server, record marked as deleted"
          },
          "response": []
